# Next.js & React Conventions

## App Router

- Dùng App Router (thư mục `app/[locale]/`)
- i18n qua `next-intl` với `[locale]` segment
- Server Components mặc định, Client Components khi cần interactivity

## Auth (Limen)

### Client

```typescript
// src/lib/limen-auth.ts
import { createAuthClient } from "limen-auth/react";
import {
  bearerPlugin,
  credentialPasswordPlugin,
  oauthClientPlugin,
} from "limen-auth/plugins";

export const authClient = createAuthClient({
  baseURL: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL,
  basePath: "/auth",
  plugins: [credentialPasswordPlugin(), oauthClientPlugin(), bearerPlugin()],
});
```

### Token cho Go APIs

Opaque Bearer từ `authClient.bearer.getTokens()?.accessToken` → `token-manager` in-memory.
**Không** dùng localStorage cho token. **Không** còn Next `/api/auth/set-session`.

```typescript
// src/lib/token-manager.ts
getToken() / setToken() / clearToken()
```

### AuthProvider

```typescript
// src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx
// login    → authClient.signIn.credential → setToken(bearer)
// register → authClient.signUp.credential
// logout   → authClient.signOut → clearToken()
// refreshSession → authClient.getSession + bearer
```

### Client-side fetch

```typescript
// src/lib/fetch-with-auth.ts
fetchWithAuth<T>(url, options)  // Authorization: Bearer từ getToken()
```

### Key Files

| File | Vai trò |
|------|---------|
| `src/lib/limen-auth.ts` | Limen auth client |
| `src/lib/token-manager.ts` | In-memory Bearer cho Go APIs |
| `src/lib/fetch-with-auth.ts` | fetch wrapper + Bearer |
| `src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx` | Auth context |
| `src/components/auth/SocialLoginButtons.tsx` | Google / Facebook / TikTok |

### OAuth callbacks (backend)

`https://api.puchi.io.vn/auth/oauth/{google|facebook|tiktok}/callback`

## Components

- **Shadcn UI** trong `components/ui/`
- Feature components trong `components/<feature>/`

## State Management

- **Zustand** cho global state
- React Context cho auth + theme/locale

## API Calls

- Auth → `authClient.*` (`credentials` / cookies tới Limen)
- Backend → `fetchWithAuth()` / `clientFetch()` với Bearer
- API base: `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`

## i18n

- `next-intl` + `useTranslations()`
- Messages trong `messages/`
- Không hardcode text trong component
